United Kingdom.title: Harmonized Index of Consumer Prices: Passenger Transport by Air for United Kingdom
United Kingdom.notes:
The Harmonized Index of Consumer Prices category "Passenger Transport by Air (07.3.3)" is a classification of services that includes transport of individuals and groups of persons and luggage by airplane and helicopter.

This category is a subcategory of the Transport (07) and of Transport Services (07.3) categories.

Information provided in the notes pertaining to HICP classifications can be found from the source at: http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/cache/metadata/en/prc_hicp_esms.htm.
